<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238675>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Eratigena laksao sp. n., male paratype habitus of living specimen (1 lateral view; 2 anterior view; 3 dorsal view; 4 same specimen as subadult, dorsal view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238675/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238676>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 13. Eratigena laksao sp. n., male holotype. 5. Carapace, dorsal view. 6. Abdomen, dorsal view. 7. Carapace and chelicerae, anterior view. 8. Sternum, ventral view. 9. Spinnerets, ventral view. 10. Chelicerae, posteroventral view. 11. Mouthpart, ventral view. 12. Coxa with trochanter and basal femora, ventral view. 13. Claws of leg 1, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238676/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238677>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 15. Eratigena laksao sp. n. 14. Left palp in ventral view (male holotype). 15. Same, retrolateral view. Abbreviations: Br = bristles; C = conductor; dRTA = dorsal branch of RTA; E = embolus; MA = median apophysis; R = membranous ridge; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis; vRTA = ventral branch of RTA." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238677/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238678>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 21. Eratigena laksao sp. n., male holotype. 16. Left palp, prolateral view. 17. Same, ventral view. 18. Same, retrolateral view. 19. Bulb of left palp, ventral view. 20. Same, retrolateral view. 21. Palpal tibia, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238678/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

